title: Fortios: Managed switch interface
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the interfaces of the connected switches of a Fortigate firewall.
 With the help of the “fortios_switch_interface_discovery_parameter” rule 
 can be used to configure the interfaces to be monitored based on the description.
 Regex must be used for this.
 The performance data is collected per interface.

 This check receives its data via a piggyback mechanism.


 The special agent is required for this check, 
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service per interface is created.
